lt;!--&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;几个月来，美国人一直在与高油价和持续通胀作斗争，导致消费者信心跌至历史低点。现在，沃尔玛和洛斯等零售商&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/VMAXUpcLBoPQEwmgp4gdXX6a8JIypeWbD3LU7_28uLtRgozpTjtAC0NppHSnHMQBFthmHHpMrCoskriAlsxROc-H0GPdDuLo8VYBVZT5OJhGDuOF94CeVNFKcAHOGJKYS2D_xh8WiwKG6qzyo75lixR6Pqpp0RioiHQhU3AoQpaaDQ6-TTaWFOiYj0pIq_S8rOR3jI-D0JKRSgqzIA7qXNjfKWYvvohX2dIbk0b4qb34kQhqUgi0sCtOb7-JN6BZ6KJwXjAQiKOXSUldEjrGdvEq5ZhxyiN0gPt6i6-PnitpROarSXQY7e7JeeW7O3lpsccQAZsll3Xcz2oVXZ7r0mzJdsa1oay3_NgbHKMJLbB5_4L8CpMC-QrjRQqQaP06zJgwOi8HKjhRBmXzM1vmY-jsWG3ZTuGn9-jCMWYIs6fCzvytcYBEIIaP1VBj9sOwOkTj2AafpiWT9X2hXP-a0sQ1z9gS_xmc21Sni-VNO56Ry4UVTxJAzeBJs2B_5SBGZ8GOpS8RfRvxQwvbF6_knVr-G8x4fys/o4LJF7a9NblaX4SveBYI2RPmk4mwNcsE/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="天然气费用上涨吓坏了消费者，通胀焦虑蔓延"&gt;越来越大声地警告称&lt;/a&gt;，美以与伊朗战争导致的燃料成本飙升将很快反映在货架上产品的价格上。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;当这种情况发生时，只会使美国的负担能力问题变得更加严重。特尔西咨询集团 (Telsey Advisory Group) 分析师乔·费尔德曼 (Joe Feldman) 表示，即使是现在，“我们仍担心消费者的消费能力下降”。展望未来，“低收入消费者将面临更大的挑战。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;沃尔玛首席财务官约翰·戴维·雷尼 (John David Rainey) 表示，该公司已经看到一些习惯发生变化：第一季度，消费者每次访问沃尔玛泵时&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/yHhmBFXlgHQ9TNLBvYpusfCCWEXSWVjvK4Wup9_0LHz9eWjkoRKFgFYx1vUrTHhnTJNxSpncr6MzFZ0HM1wfLKQj9CFiJXJesHWGdr_SLvezOTo6HlYFtRSt8achMVbWDnilP8e2bWxiyhuDMF3LLSPLEeWE9Ywdb_QeUIQxTTHqy70woX8UojJd9hoz8uDc3yCV6yPuE0YH183KTN14BPsSEAGMRCkoPYYuJBcVgJvZIBSLcthr2od94pn3pb9NwlbJ4RVRCDi6ndT2hmpF5rLYbNC-_lF2ezKpe06B9wxwmR8jOlNY5vTHjxkNlTuwHD0qIx-bcZA5eDudWISJJbYLRP4uPX1LoafiTftKpup9mn811jR_GJYbLkCUzT8BvMMf0sJFfse_UBKIPluYmkBiLaQHYNZoJuWTabRT8HsB7oeNdt9kRrPpY__eMsCax7zkJTgNEYb5b2jGsYTFjWQ3flfTLpgtchmF-vkJbNw-gm9CNELwhDdNQuUeKqIK5ndpu3EWluzgaZiJEMiNUrzlBTSQCg/K_kkpMuNoiN83p2Vobh5jLy24YjYujn-/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="沃尔玛表示